About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalalâ€™s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Superman | Official Trailer | DC
snippet.description:
Your choices, your actions, thatâ€™s what makes you who you are. #Superman - Only In Theaters and @Imax July 11

â€œSuperman,â€ DC Studiosâ€™ first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures.  In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman whoâ€™s driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind. 

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (â€œTwisters,â€ â€œHollywoodâ€) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (â€œThe Marvelous Mrs. Maiselâ€) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the â€œX-Menâ€ movies, â€œJuror #2â€) as Lex Luthor.  The film also stars Edi Gathegi (â€œFor All Mankindâ€), Anthony Carrigan (â€œBarry,â€ â€œGothamâ€), Nathan Fillion (the â€œGuardians of the Galaxyâ€ films, â€œThe Suicide Squadâ€), Isabela Merced (â€œAlien Romulusâ€), Skyler Gisondo (â€œLicorice Pizza,â€ â€œBooksmartâ€), Sara Sampaio (â€œAt Midnightâ€), MarÃ­a Gabriela de FarÃ­a (â€œThe Moodysâ€), Wendell Pierce (â€œSelma,â€ â€œTom Clancyâ€™s Jack Ryanâ€), Alan Tudyk (â€œAndorâ€), Pruitt Taylor Vince (â€œBird Boxâ€) and Neva Howell (â€œGreedy Peopleâ€).

â€œSupermanâ€ is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther.  Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with composer David Fleming (â€œThe Last of Usâ€) and editors William Hoy (â€œThe Batmanâ€) and Craig Alpert (â€œDeadpool 2,â€ â€œBlue Beetleâ€).  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment/The Safran Company Production, A James Gunn Film, â€œSuperman,â€ which will be in theaters and IMAXÂ® nationwide on July 11, 2025, and internationally beginning 9 July 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.title: chann se jo toota mera sapna
snippet.description:
A couple of months ago I had promised myself that I will take up YouTube more seriously. Creating content in the last seven years has been really fulfilling. Par YT par kabhi regularly aur shiddat se content nahi banaya. As a professional yapper, I realised I have a lot more to say, write, share and perform. Aur kahin se toh shuru karna hee padega. 

So, with the resolve that har saturday ek nayi video (hey mata rani, please saath dijiye), I am so happy to share this. Bahut zyada he honest video hai. Enjoy please.

Follow me on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/kushakapila?igsh=MTJscmJ5aXFxeTZobQ%3D%3D&utm_source=qr

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Churake - Vilen X Kanika Kapoor (Official Video)
snippet.description:
â€˜Churake' is a song about a cosmopolitan city girl who falls for a traditional desi guy. As she tries to express her feelings, he consistently pushes her away, burdened by family responsibilities and hesitant to get entangled in a complicated romance. All of this is happening in a delightful, coming-of-age manner.

Artist : Vilen, Kanika Kapoor
Lyrcist : Vilen
Composer : Vilen
Music : Vilen, Gaurav Pahuja
Director : Vilen
Female lead : Sakshi Sobhya
Screenplay : Vilen
Editor : Vilen
DOP : Alex
Color Correction : Vilen
Make up Artist : Dinky Magoo
Mix Master : Hanish Taneja
Music programming : Maniac
Recording studio : G10 Studio, Yash Raj Studios
Curation Partner : Rtist91
Casting : Amit Om Malik

Label : Darks Music Company

Lyrics -

Ankhiyan milake na baaeri tu
Battiyan bujha ke na ja na

Ratiyan jagake bhi tu
mere samne na ra

Sakhiyan chidaein pal pal
Meri saans chadhake na ja na

Ratiyan jagake bhi tu
Mere samne na ra


Na chaal sharabi dekhunga
Na baat nawabi phekunga

Simple saada su chora
Tere haath main aaun na

Tu kyu itraave re chori
Tanne aankh bhi tha ke dekhun na

Manne saaf rehne de
Mann mai mere meil chadhave na

Manne kaam bade se karne
Mere kandhe pe bojh do baatan ka

Sada izzat se karvaani
Kade naak kataani na


Ankhiyan milake na baaeri tu
Battiyan bujha ke na ja na

Ratiyan jagake bhi tu
mere samne na ra

Sakhiyan chidaein pal pal
Meri saans chadhake na ja na

Ratiyan jagake bhi tu
Mere samne na ra


Tellyphone laga lena
Tu teri diwani ko

Mai jaan nahi mangu
Banjau teri kahani jo

Manne time nahi chori
Deewani baton ka

Na ashik mai na karna
Koe showk kharabi ka

Ho jaungi teri tu tera rang chadha dena
Dhal jaungi tujhsi jeene ka dhang bta dena

Main tuta hoya gilaas su
Mujhmai jaam bhare kyu khamekha

Sab bikhra bikhra handega
Fer naam lagaiye na

snippet.description:
naya saal naya maal

ğŸ”¥ Subscribe for Tabahi Videos

Android 16 is the next major leap in Googleâ€™s mobile OS, bringing a wave of AI-powered features, privacy upgrades, and performance improvements to Android smartphones in 2025. With a strong focus on context-aware intelligence, cross-device fluidity, and smoother multitasking, Android 16 is designed to power the next generation of smartphones, tablets, and foldables.

ğŸ” Top Features of Android 16:

Gemini AI Integration: Smart reply, live summarization, AI-assisted typing, and app-aware suggestions built into the OS.

Lock Screen Widgets 2.0: Deeper customization, glanceable info, and always-on productivity.

Better Background Activity Control: Improved battery life with smarter app hibernation and process management.

Privacy Dashboard 2.0: Real-time app access tracking for microphone, camera, and location usage.

Universal App Streaming: Continue apps seamlessly across Android, ChromeOS, and Windows.

AI-Powered Multilingual Typing: Automatically detects and adapts to the language youâ€™re typing in without switching keyboards.

Revamped Material You Design: Even more dynamic theming, contrast improvements, and adaptive animations.

Improved Foldable & Tablet Support: Enhanced taskbar, split-screen gestures, and large-screen app optimizations.

Android 16 will begin rolling out in beta versions by mid-2025, with the Pixel 9 series and top flagships from Samsung, OnePlus, iQOO, and Vivo among the first to get it.

If you're searching for Android 16 features list, Android 16 eligible devices, or wondering how it compares to iOS 18, this deep dive covers everything you need to know about Google's most intelligent Android version yet.

snippet.title: Justice Bhushan Ramkrishna Gavai takes the oath as the 52nd Chief Justice of India | 14 May 2025
snippet.description:
#chiefjusticeofindia   #supremecourt #cji  #rashtrapatibhavan

Dis: Justice Bhushan Ramkrishna Gavai takes the oath as the 52nd Chief Justice of India, marking a significant chapter in the nation's judicial journey.

President Draupadi Murmu administered the oath of the office of the Chief Justice of India (CJI) to Supreme Court judge Justice  Bhushan Ramkrishna Gavai on Wednesday (14.05.2025)

In a ceremony graced by Vice-President Jagdeep Dhankhar, and Prime Minister Narendra Modi, the new CJI began his tenure with dignity and resolve

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.
